// ... later, on shutdown:
if (sseServer) {
  // Only close if it actually bound successfully.
  // Check `listening` flag because the server object exists even if bind failed.
  if (sseServer.listening) {
    await new Promise<void>((resolve) => sseServer.close(() => resolve()));
  }
}
```

For tests, pass an ephemeral port explicitly:

```ts
